### **Summary: Bottlenecks & Optimization Opportunities**

| Function | Bottleneck | Severity | Optimization Strategy |
|----------|-----------|----------|----------------------|
| groupByCategory | array.find + reduce per insert | HIGH | Replace with Map, track running total |
| findDuplicates | O(n²) comparison + duplicate tracking | CRITICAL | Use Set of keys, single-pass tracking |
| calculateRunningBalance | Rescan/re-sort/recalc per position | CRITICAL | Single pass: filter once, sort once, cumulative balance |
| topSpenders | Multiple scans + bubble sort | HIGH | Single map pass, Array.sort with comparator |
